                            <comment id="15269671" author="wushujames" created="Tue, 3 May 2016 21:50:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We ran into this today. While we are waiting for the 0.10 release, is there anything we can do to work around this bug?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
